description.en:
Stealth launched, X Æ A-12 is one of a kind. Representation of a dream, of a vision. Representation of a decentralized society. A ""Thank you"" to Elon Musk. Our end goal is making the world a better place, which is why charity donations are part of our roadmap.
Pronounced as ""X-Ash-A-Twelve"".
The smart contracts have been developed and tested thoroughly. There is a strong team of 7 people on board. Our team consists of 7 people. 3 developers, with 1 smart contract developer and 1 web developer. 2 community leads. 2 people in the marketing team. The team is split between EU & the US.
Detailed roadmap can be seen on the website. What the future beholds cannot be more exciting.
